filesharing.core.client

Class FileTransfer

  • java.lang.Object
    • filesharing.core.client.FileTransfer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class FileTransfer
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This represents a file transfer - information about the file (file size, block size, etc.) and the current state of the file transfer (how many blocks have been downloaded, if it is currently downloading/seeding)
    See Also:
